I've discovered a critical logic error in `App.tsx`: a missing closing brace in the `handleLogout` function has caused the subsequent functions to be nested inside it. This is a clear syntax error in the TSX itself. While the "Unexpected token 'export'" error often arises from bundling or browser misinterpretations, this seems to be the root cause of the unexpected error. I'm focusing on the code compilation now, to determine how this error has manifested, with `index.html` referencing `index.tsx`, which contains the `App.tsx` errors.


