I can now confirm the missing `<script type="module" src="index.tsx"></script>` tag in `index.html`. While the environment *may* handle injection, the provided setup clearly lacks this crucial import, making the ES6 module interpretation impossible. The prompt mentioned automatic importing. I am now examining how this is supposed to work. This explains the 'Unexpected token 'export'' error perfectly. Also, `App.tsx` has critical errors.


