I'm now certain the core issue stems from that missing brace in `App.tsx` and the lack of a `<script type="module">` tag in `index.html`. While the initial assumption of automatic importing was misleading, the critical syntax error in `App.tsx` is the primary culprit. Fixing that must come first. The structure of the html file needs to be verified.

